        </Style>
        <ZIndex>16</ZIndex>
        <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
        <Left>0.375in</Left>
        <Height>0.25in</Height>
        <Value>SAVE WATER FOR NATION</Value>
      </Textbox>
      <Textbox Name="textbox28">
        <Top>5.75in</Top>
        <Width>8in</Width>
        <Style>
          <FontFamily>Courier New</FontFamily>
          <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
          <PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft>
          <PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight>
          <PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop>
          <PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom>
        </Style>
        <ZIndex>15</ZIndex>
        <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
        <Left>0.125in</Left>
        <Height>2.125in</Height>
        <Value>="1.  Payment shall be made by Cash or DD in favour of ‘NOIDA’ directly in HDFC &amp; ICICI Bank any branches of Noida"+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"2. Consumer can also pay Water Bill Online at official website of Noida i.e. www.noidaauthorityonline.com ."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"3.  If amount has already been deposited then,The demand is treated as withdrawn and submit the photocopy of the deposited challan to the office."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"4.  The water connection shall be disconnected if payment is not made upto due date without any further notice."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"5.  For any Clarification / error please contact to the office of the Project Engineer water work's compound "+Fields!Div_type.Value+" between 10.30 a.m. to 1.00 p.m. on all working days"+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"6.  This is  a computer generated demand which requires no signature."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"7.  E &amp; O E."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"8. For any other information visit the WebSite http://noidaauthorityonline.com"</Value>
      </Textbox>
